 &lt;img src="https://blog-pic-ck.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/posts/zh/ml-math-derivations/20-%e6%ad%a3%e5%88%99%e5%8c%96%e4%b8%8e%e6%a8%a1%e5%9e%8b%e9%80%89%e6%8b%a9/illustration_1.jpg" alt="机器学习数学推导（第 20 篇）：正则化与模型选择 —— 图示" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="content-image">
 
